  ('optometrist-moex-01788', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳驗光師發現李小姐配戴單焦眼鏡於正常頂點距離看遠時，需要讓眼鏡往眼睛方向推才會更清楚，且李小 姐自述戴眼鏡看遠比不戴清楚。陳驗光師拿起眼鏡觀察，發現在某一特定距離時，看到的影像是倒立且縮 小，試問李小姐眼睛的屈光狀態及眼鏡的狀況為何？', '["近視，眼鏡度數過多負度數", "近視，眼鏡度數過多正度數", "遠視，眼鏡度數過多負度數", "遠視，眼鏡度數過多正度數"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-01789', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '球柱面透鏡屈光力以正交圓柱面形式表示為+5.00DC×090合併+4.00DC×180，與下列那種表示法相同？', '["+4.00DS/+1.00DC×090", "+4.00DS/-1.00DC×090", "+5.00DC/+1.00DC×180", "+1.00DC/-1.00DC×180"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-01790', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '單焦（monofocal）鏡片要加上稜鏡度數，下列何種製作方式比較不適合？', '["鏡片偏心製作（decenteredprism）", "鏡片稜鏡研磨（ground-inprism）", "加上菲涅耳稜鏡（Fresnelprism）", "切除式稜鏡（slab-offprism）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
